POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Course Details Get 3796 POINTER
SELECT A.CRSE_ID , A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR , B.EFFDT , A.STRM , A.SESSION_CODE , A.CLASS_NBR , CASE WHEN B.COURSE_APPROVED = 'A' AND B.SCHEDULE_COURSE = 'Y' THEN 'Active' ELSE 'Inactive' END , C.DESCR , C.FEES_EXIST , C.UNITS_MINIMUM , C.UNITS_MAXIMUM , C.GRADING_BASIS , C.COURSE_TITLE_LONG , B.SUBJECT , B.CATALOG_NBR , B.RQRMNT_GROUP , C.DESCRLONG , A.START_DT , A.END_DT , rtrim(REPLACE( %Substring(C.descrlong, CASE WHEN instr(C.descrlong, 'C-ID') = 0 THEN LENGTH(C.descrlong)+1 ELSE instr(C.descrlong, 'C-ID')+5 END) ,'-' , ' ') , '.') , CN.SC_MIS_CRSE_ID , TS.CRSE_ATTR_VALUE , CS.CRSE_ATTR_VALUE FROM %Table(CLASS_TBL) A JOIN %Table(CRSE_OFFER) B ON (A.CRSE_ID = B.CRSE_ID AND A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND A.INSTITUTION = B.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = B.ACAD_CAREER) JOIN %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) C ON (B.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = C.EFFDT) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(SC_CRSE_OFFR_ID) CN ON (B.CRSE_ID = CN.CRSE_ID AND B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = CN.CRSE_OFFER_NBR) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CRSE_ATTRIBUTES) TS ON (B.CRSE_ID = TS.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = TS.EFFDT) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CRSE_ATTRIBUTES) CS ON (B.CRSE_ID = CS.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = CS.EFFDT) WHERE (LTRIM(RTRIM(A.SUBJECT)) %Concat '-' %Concat LTRIM(RTRIM(A.CATALOG_NBR))) = :1 AND A.STRM = :2 AND A.INSTITUTION = :3 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :4 AND C.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND C.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(C_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) C_ED WHERE C_ED.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND C_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND C_ED.EFFDT <= A.START_DT) AND (CN.EFFDT IS NULL OR CN.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(CN_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(SC_CRSE_OFFR_ID) CN_ED WHERE CN_ED.CRSE_ID = CN.CRSE_ID AND CN_ED.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = CN.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND CN_ED.EFFDT <= B.EFFDT)) AND (TS.CRSE_ATTR IS NULL OR TS.CRSE_ATTR = :5) AND (CS.CRSE_ATTR IS NULL OR CS.CRSE_ATTR = :6)
254 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves a single course offering (class) detail record for a given course and term
0 HANDLE
GBL 55 7 1900-01-01
3806 POINTER
SELECT A.CRSE_ID , A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR , B.EFFDT , A.STRM , A.SESSION_CODE , A.CLASS_NBR , CASE WHEN B.COURSE_APPROVED = 'A' AND B.SCHEDULE_COURSE = 'Y' THEN 'Active' ELSE 'Inactive' END , C.DESCR , C.FEES_EXIST , C.UNITS_MINIMUM , C.UNITS_MAXIMUM , C.GRADING_BASIS , C.COURSE_TITLE_LONG , B.SUBJECT , B.CATALOG_NBR , B.RQRMNT_GROUP , C.DESCRLONG , A.START_DT , A.END_DT , rtrim(REPLACE( %Substring(C.descrlong, CASE WHEN CHARINDEX(C.descrlong, 'C-ID') = 0 THEN LEN(C.descrlong)+1 ELSE CHARINDEX(C.descrlong, 'C-ID')+5 END) ,'-' , ' ') , '.') , CN.SC_MIS_CRSE_ID , TS.CRSE_ATTR_VALUE , CS.CRSE_ATTR_VALUE FROM %Table(CLASS_TBL) A JOIN %Table(CRSE_OFFER) B ON (A.CRSE_ID = B.CRSE_ID AND A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND A.INSTITUTION = B.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = B.ACAD_CAREER) JOIN %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) C ON (B.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = C.EFFDT) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(SC_CRSE_OFFR_ID) CN ON (B.CRSE_ID = CN.CRSE_ID AND B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = CN.CRSE_OFFER_NBR) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CRSE_ATTRIBUTES) TS ON (B.CRSE_ID = TS.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = TS.EFFDT) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CRSE_ATTRIBUTES) CS ON (B.CRSE_ID = CS.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = CS.EFFDT) WHERE (LTRIM(RTRIM(A.SUBJECT)) %Concat '-' %Concat LTRIM(RTRIM(A.CATALOG_NBR))) = :1 AND A.STRM = :2 AND A.INSTITUTION = :3 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :4 AND C.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND C.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(C_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) C_ED WHERE C_ED.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND C_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND C_ED.EFFDT <= A.START_DT) AND (CN.EFFDT IS NULL OR CN.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(CN_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(SC_CRSE_OFFR_ID) CN_ED WHERE CN_ED.CRSE_ID = CN.CRSE_ID AND CN_ED.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = CN.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND CN_ED.EFFDT <= B.EFFDT)) AND (TS.CRSE_ATTR IS NULL OR TS.CRSE_ATTR = :5) AND (CS.CRSE_ATTR IS NULL OR CS.CRSE_ATTR = :6)

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Course Requisites 1936 POINTER
SELECT A.RQRMNT_GROUP , A.DESCRLONG , CX.SUBJECT , CX.CATALOG_NBR , B.SAA_DESCRLONG , B.REQUISITE_TYPE FROM %Table(RQ_GRP_TBL) A JOIN %Table(RQ_GRP_DETL_TBL) B ON (A.RQRMNT_GROUP = B.RQRMNT_GROUP AND A.EFFDT = B.EFFDT) LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT C.CRSE_ID , C.SUBJECT , C.CATALOG_NBR FROM %Table(CRSE_OFFER) C WHERE C.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(C_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(CRSE_OFFER) C_ED WHERE C.CRSE_ID = C_ED.CRSE_ID AND C.EFFDT <= %DateIn(:2)) AND C.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = ( SELECT MIN(C_OF.CRSE_OFFER_NBR) FROM %Table(CRSE_OFFER) C_OF WHERE C.CRSE_ID = C_OF.CRSE_ID AND C.EFFDT = C_OF.EFFDT) AND C.INSTITUTION = :3 AND C.ACAD_CAREER = :4) CX ON (B.CRSE_ID = CX.CRSE_ID) WHERE A.RQRMNT_GROUP = :1 AND A.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(A_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(RQ_GRP_TBL) A_ED WHERE A_ED.RQRMNT_GROUP = A.RQRMNT_GROUP AND A_ED.EFFDT <= %DateIn(LTRIM(:2))) AND A.INSTITUTION = :3 AND A.RQRMNT_USEAGE = 'ENR' AND A.EFF_STATUS = 'A'
604 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves a listing of course requisites, both prerequisite and corequisites, for a given requirement group (that has been previously pulled from the course details). For course requirements, returns the first course offering available for a given requirement
0 HANDLE

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Section Instructors 1358 POINTER
SELECT DISTINCT A.EMPLID , B.FIRST_NAME , B.LAST_NAME , E.EMAIL_ADDR FROM %Table(CLASS_INSTR) A JOIN %Table(NAMES) B ON (A.EMPLID = B.EMPLID) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(EMAIL_ADDRESSES) E ON (B.EMPLID = E.EMPLID) WHERE A.CRSE_ID = :1 AND A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = :2 AND A.STRM = :3 AND A.SESSION_CODE = :4 AND A.CLASS_SECTION = :5 AND A.SCHED_PRINT_INSTR = 'Y' AND B.NAME_TYPE = 'PRI' AND B.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND B.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(B_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(NAMES) B_ED WHERE B_ED.EMPLID = B.EMPLID AND B_ED.NAME_TYPE = B.NAME_TYPE AND B_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND B_ED.EFFDT <= %CurrentDateTimeIn) AND COALESCE(E.PREF_EMAIL_FLAG, 'Y') = 'Y'
220 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves distinct listing of instructors for a given class section
0 HANDLE

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Section Base Get 1642 POINTER
SELECT A.STRM , A.SESSION_CODE , A.CRSE_ID , A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR , A.SUBJECT , A.CATALOG_NBR , A.CLASS_NBR , A.CLASS_SECTION , A.CLASS_STAT , A.DESCR , A.ENRL_CAP , A.WAIT_CAP , A.CAMPUS , A.SSR_COMPONENT , A.INSTRUCTION_MODE , B.UNITS_MINIMUM , B.UNITS_MAXIMUM , A.START_DT , A.END_DT , S.WEEKS_OF_INSTRUCT FROM %Table(CLASS_TBL) A , %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) B , %Table(SESSION_TBL) S WHERE A.STRM = :1 AND A.INSTITUTION = :2 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :3 AND A.CRSE_ID = B.CRSE_ID AND B.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(B_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(CRSE_CATALOG) B_ED WHERE B_ED.CRSE_ID = B.CRSE_ID AND B_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND B_ED.EFFDT <= A.START_DT) AND A.INSTITUTION = S.INSTITUTION AND A.ACAD_CAREER = S.ACAD_CAREER AND A.STRM = S.STRM AND A.SESSION_CODE = S.SESSION_CODE
452 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Provides the base query for retrieving class section details for a given term. Additional Where clauses are added to filter the results by either course, section, or list of sections.
0 HANDLE

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Section Meeting Patterns 998 POINTER
SELECT A.CLASS_MTG_NBR , %TimeOut(%TimePart(A.MEETING_TIME_START)) , %TimeOut(%TimePart(A.MEETING_TIME_END)) , A.MON , A.TUES , A.WED , A.THURS , A.FRI , A.SAT , A.SUN , %DateOut(A.START_DT) , %DateOut(A.END_DT) , B.BLDG_CD , B.ROOM , B.LOCATION FROM %Table(CLASS_MTG_PAT) A LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(FACILITY_TBL) B ON (A.FACILITY_ID = B.FACILITY_ID) WHERE A.CRSE_ID = :1 AND A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = :2 AND A.STRM = :3 AND A.SESSION_CODE = :4 AND A.CLASS_SECTION = :5
230 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Retrieves a list of meeting patterns for a given term and class section.
0 HANDLE

POINTER
GBL 32
1900-01-01 CCTC Section Search Base Get 2694 POINTER
SELECT DISTINCT A.CLASS_NBR FROM %Table(CLASS_TBL) A LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CLASS_MTG_PAT) B ON (A.CRSE_ID = B.CRSE_ID AND A.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND A.STRM = B.STRM AND A.SESSION_CODE = B.SESSION_CODE AND A.CLASS_SECTION = B.CLASS_SECTION) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(CLASS_INSTR) C ON (B.CRSE_ID = C.CRSE_ID AND B.CRSE_OFFER_NBR = C.CRSE_OFFER_NBR AND B.STRM = C.STRM AND B.SESSION_CODE = C.SESSION_CODE AND B.CLASS_SECTION = C.CLASS_SECTION AND B.CLASS_MTG_NBR = C.CLASS_MTG_NBR) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(NAMES) N ON (C.EMPLID = N.EMPLID) LEFT OUTER JOIN %Table(FACILITY_TBL) F ON (B.FACILITY_ID = F.FACILITY_ID) WHERE A.STRM = :1 AND A.INSTITUTION = :2 AND A.ACAD_CAREER = :3 AND COALESCE(C.SCHED_PRINT_INSTR, 'Y') = 'Y' AND COALESCE(N.NAME_TYPE, 'PRI') = 'PRI' AND COALESCE(N.EFF_STATUS, 'A') = 'A' AND (N.EFFDT IS NULL OR N.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(N_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(NAMES) N_ED WHERE N_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND N_ED.EMPLID = N.EMPLID AND N_ED.NAME_TYPE = N.NAME_TYPE AND N_ED.EFFDT <= %CurrentDateTimeIn)) AND COALESCE(F.EFF_STATUS, 'A') = 'A' AND (F.EFFDT IS NULL OR F.EFFDT = ( SELECT MAX(F_ED.EFFDT) FROM %Table(FACILITY_TBL) F_ED WHERE F_ED.EFF_STATUS = 'A' AND F_ED.SETID = F.SETID AND F_ED.FACILITY_ID = F.FACILITY_ID AND F_ED.EFFDT <= B.START_DT))
582 POINTER
California Community Colleges Tech Center: Provides the base query for searching for class sections within a given term. Further Where Clauses are added to filter the search by given key terms (aka search phrases). Provides a distinct list of class_nbrs to do a full details retrieve against
0 HANDLE
